Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.70,0:01:36.33,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,, 说是由于要举办联合的君主会议
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.66,0:01:38.75,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,让我去一趟哈鲁西亚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.50,0:01:42.67,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,距离大圣堂的惨剧已有半年有余
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.67,0:01:44.21,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这才想着开会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.00,0:01:46.80,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说没什么兴趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.84,0:01:48.26,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不过也只能去了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.26,0:01:53.39,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟刚发生主事件的时候大家都在观察动向嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.47,0:01:57.06,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,也许是因为您在塞维斯一站中搭救了提欧阁下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.60,0:02:01.19,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我个人认为维拉尔阁下理应受到称赞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.77,0:02:02.94,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这可不好说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.82,0:02:06.32,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,当上联合盟主阿莱克希斯阁下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.82,0:02:09.03,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不希望与同盟对决
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.03,0:02:14.87,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,话说  你生日是哪天呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.71,0:02:27.92,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害居然能同时操作多个对象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.97,0:02:33.97,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,只要拿握了诀窍这可是很简单的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.39,0:02:36.93,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,请教教我吧 拜托了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.02,0:02:40.19,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛…我倒是无所谓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.27,0:02:42.10,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.66,0:02:58.08,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.91,0:03:04.79,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,纪念玛格丽特二十五岁生日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.17,0:03:07.42,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,恕我直言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.00,0:03:12.68,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,维拉尔大人为我们的第二段人生着想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.80,0:03:14.22,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这让人很高兴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.43,0:03:20.06,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,可是玛格丽特阁下希望继续履行与伯爵的契约
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.48,0:03:22.52,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,真是这样的话我就很开心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.27,0:03:28.02,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  我可不能区别对待她一人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.99,0:03:37.08,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,西露卡抓紧准备玛格丽特的庆生会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.53,0:03:39.95,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,另外你提欧以及拉席克阁下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.25,0:03:43.71,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,得跟我一同前去参加将于近期举办君主会议
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.17,0:03:46.29,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,提欧大人也要去吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.29,0:03:51.13,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,西斯迪纳子爵佩提力克•罗西尼子爵也会出席会议
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.30,0:03:53.05,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,见一面应该没损失才对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.51,0:03:55.39,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,感谢您的用心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.59,0:03:56.93,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,用不着道谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.35,0:04:00.22,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,最主要的理由是为了让你们作证
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.35,0:04:02.73,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,战争的导火索是你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.69,0:04:05.69,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是协助而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.27,0:04:07.81,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这是当然的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.36,0:04:09.36,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那就麻烦你们了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.45,0:04:25.67,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,玛格丽特阁下生日快乐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.92,0:04:27.54,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,生日快乐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.46,0:04:32.76,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,承蒙照顾了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.96,0:04:35.34,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来打算回老家吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.63,0:04:36.26,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.68,0:04:40.26,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,真够艳丽的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.51,0:04:42.35,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来还要跳舞哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.89,0:04:45.27,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,提欧大人跳舞厉害吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.52,0:04:48.69,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能连看今晚都是第一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.94,0:04:51.77,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,梅蕾蒂斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.36,0:04:54.69,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,玛格丽特阁下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.78,0:04:59.24,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,生日... 快乐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.53,0:05:04.08,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你这是什么表情 西露卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.75,0:05:08.88,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我还想向玛格丽特阁下请教很多东西呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.00,0:05:12.55,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,教你？我可是业火的玛格丽特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.92,0:05:16.26,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,除了野蛮的元素魔法就没什么可教你的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.92,0:05:20.09,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟我还远远不够成熟啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.22,0:05:24.89,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你虽然不是维拉尔大人的契约魔法师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.10,0:05:26.77,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 你不仅给伯爵添麻烦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.85,0:05:28.35,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,还欠下了恩情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.15,0:05:30.94,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.19,0:05:36.11,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔图克和维拉尔就交给你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.98,0:07:33.06,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么看都很般配啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.81,0:07:34.60,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,的确
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.35,0:07:39.82,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 这事外人是无论如何都无法插手的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.78,0:07:43.57,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,来跳舞吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.61,0:07:45.99,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,现在吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.57,0:07:49.58,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,他们跳了那么棒的舞  就只有现在了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.17,0:08:01.88,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.59,0:08:11.39,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,123请配合这个节奏移动脚步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.89,0:08:13.06,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.27,0:08:17.73,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,再贴近我一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.98,0:08:18.81,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,可以吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.07,0:08:21.86,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,跳舞就是这样的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.20,0:08:25.86,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,贴太近了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.62,0:08:29.66,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,太近了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.79,0:08:37.63,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,看着感觉倒是蛮简单的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.46,0:08:40.00,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟是第一次嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.25,0:08:41.92,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,真是有趣的即兴表演
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.51,0:08:46.68,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,比起君主 你更有小丑的才能吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.26,0:08:48.64,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,即便是小丑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.80,0:08:51.35,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,只要能获得米尔扎阁下的认可
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.47,0:08:53.43,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,就能当成一生的荣耀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.06,0:08:58.94,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我果然看不惯你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.31,0:09:01.61,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微赏个脸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.53,0:09:10.16,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,想不到竟然连盾都带上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.45,0:09:11.66,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,尽管放马过来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.37,0:09:15.20,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.51,0:09:32.14,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我还想着比剑呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.18,0:09:33.51,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,想不到竟然只会防守
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.72,0:09:37.31,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我自认这就是我的战斗方式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.48,0:09:40.48,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这可不是君主的战斗方式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.03,0:09:46.28,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,盾能保护的只有自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.99,0:09:48.53,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,只要击败了敌人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.53,0:09:48.57,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,只要击败了敌人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.57,0:09:49.03,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,只要击败了敌人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.07,0:09:50.87,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,自己人就不会被击败
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.57,0:09:53.78,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,就结果而言能拯救众多自己人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.91,0:09:54.99,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这才是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.99,0:09:55.04,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这才是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.04,0:09:55.08,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这才是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.08,0:09:55.33,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这才是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.33,0:09:55.37,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这才是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.37,0:09:55.45,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这才是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.45,0:09:55.49,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这才是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.49,0:09:55.62,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这才是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.62,0:09:55.70,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这才是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.70,0:09:55.87,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这才是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.46,0:09:59.92,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,君主该有的战斗方式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.69,0:10:23.61,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,感谢赐教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.15,0:10:26.40,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,就因为世上净是你这种君主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.65,0:10:29.03,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,混沌的时代才会没完没了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.61,0:10:32.16,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,能获得皇帝圣印的就只有一人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.70,0:10:34.91,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,既然如此 那就尽快用战争决岀那人便是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.45,0:10:39.04,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你们这些既没野心也没有保护自己人的气概的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.21,0:10:40.62,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,没资格当君主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.67,0:10:45.38,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经决定好前路了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.38,0:10:49.97,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,迄今为止被你煽动众多人们失去了生命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.22,0:10:52.13,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,而且想必今后也一样吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.14,0:10:54.55,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,也许是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.35,0:10:59.85,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你打算踏上霸王之道对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.57,0:11:13.20,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,终有一日我会成为将当上皇帝之人的利刃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.74,0:11:17.99,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我倒是期待维拉尔阁下能获得我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.46,0:11:24.46,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我完全看不到活下来的希望啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.17,0:11:26.21,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我也一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.50,0:11:30.26,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,在那人走过的路上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.42,0:11:32.22,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,想必会留下一路的敌人尸体吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.13,0:11:35.68,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我走过的路上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.76,0:11:38.18,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,或许会留下自己人的尸体啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.85,0:11:41.06,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟这就是王道嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.56,0:11:44.69,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不想走那种路啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.06,0:11:50.99,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,提欧大人拥有让人产生共鸣团结一致的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.53,0:11:54.41,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说提欧大人前进的路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.53,0:11:59.70,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,源于与让饱受混沌和暴政折磨的人们分享情感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.79,0:12:04.25,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说这不是我一个人的路啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.04,0:12:10.05,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你也会陪我踏上这条路的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.42,0:12:11.55,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那是当然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.26,0:12:21.93,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,感谢您举办了一场美妙的庆生会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.93,0:12:24.69,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,如果让我说真心话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.98,0:12:27.06,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我还想继续为您效劳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.69,0:12:29.61,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你能这么说我很开心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.11,0:12:33.74,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,只不过  你是崇拜圣火的教团的巫女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.49,0:12:36.24,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,要是一直把你留在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.53,0:12:39.03,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,达尔塔尼亚的大众可是会发出抗议的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.95,0:12:40.99,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,说真心话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.45,0:12:43.87,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我还想再让你献一段时间策
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.83,0:12:47.42,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟能商量外交事宜的人也就只有你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.13,0:12:50.04,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,一不留神就仰仗你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.21,0:12:52.80,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,真是倍感开心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.30,0:12:57.72,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,军事外交的事宜我认为还是西露卡靠谱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.09,0:13:00.60,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,内政就交给下一任魔法师长劳拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.72,0:13:02.26,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,她完全能够胜任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.97,0:13:04.23,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,西露卡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.81,0:13:09.86,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,她为何会如此反感我呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.69,0:13:17.20,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,她似乎轻信了埃兰姆流传的好色伯爵的传言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.49,0:13:18.49,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,真过分啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.78,0:13:23.37,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得比我更珍惜女性的人可不多啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.04,0:13:25.91,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这一点我可不敢苟同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.25,0:13:27.92,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我没珍惜你吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.33,0:13:32.96,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,您只是不想深交吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.26,0:13:37.59,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,很美吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.05,0:13:40.34,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,弗劳利亚大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.05,0:13:42.81,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,曾经创建了同盟的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.10,0:13:46.02,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,铁血伯爵尤根・克莱榭的女儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.56,0:13:51.40,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯她嫁入了当时归属同盟的康斯坦斯家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.90,0:13:57.70,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我父亲利修安希望加入联合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.95,0:14:00.20,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,她无法回到克莱榭家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.32,0:14:03.41,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,被软禁的母亲极度憎恨父亲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.29,0:14:06.66,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,进而开始虐待我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.00,0:14:14.21,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,母亲无法原谅我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.88,0:14:17.80,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你身上流淌有康斯坦斯家的肮脏血脉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.26,0:14:21.84,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,母亲跟我说我根本不是她的儿子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.26,0:14:25.43,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.93,0:14:29.31,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我对母亲最久远的记忆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.27,0:14:35.98,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我当时憎恨妈妈  还诅咒了克莱榭家的血脉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.28,0:14:38.36,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,然后非常尊敬父亲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.07,0:14:42.82,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,为何现在又尊敬弗劳利亚大人了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.32,0:14:45.66,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,没多复杂的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.29,0:14:52.42,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,母亲认为父亲终有一日会畏惧我身上的克莱榭家的血脉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.00,0:14:55.42,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,而且大家都说我像母亲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.54,0:14:56.30,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.84,0:14:59.51,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,弗劳利亚大人是不想让维拉尔大人遭受危害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.67,0:15:01.47,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,才故意拒绝您的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.13,0:15:04.18,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,真相就不得而知了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.60,0:15:07.77,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不过与其恨一个生下我的女性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.52,0:15:10.81,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不觉得更应该爱她吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.35,0:15:14.40,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,维拉尔大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.06,0:15:16.86,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不要哭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.03,0:15:21.70,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说我才不愿提起这件事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.49,0:15:25.99,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直很仰慕您
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.70,0:15:30.25,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你是一名比任何人都值得信赖的女性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.00,0:15:34.17,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不过尽管我尊敬女性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.33,0:15:36.54,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,也许潜意识里还是有些畏惧吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.29,0:15:42.22,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,因此我无法娶你为妃这事从一开始就很明确了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.88,0:15:48.10,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我期盼的就只有永远陪在您身边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.43,0:15:53.64,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,祝你幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.24,0:16:04.66,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,君主会议即将于哈鲁西亚举办
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.20,0:16:07.74,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,当然我们也必须参加
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.03,0:16:11.04,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,换做往常我就乘船过去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.37,0:16:14.37,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不过这次在一个讨厌大海的魔法师的建议下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.50,0:16:17.00,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我决定跟大家一起走陆路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.71,0:16:24.43,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,等其他机会再向大家介绍我的海上宫殿好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.68,0:16:27.80,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,西露卡 再说明一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.14,0:16:29.35,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.93,0:16:33.68,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,因披席克大人平定了塞维斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.93,0:16:38.77,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,接壤的弗维斯和克劳维斯的众君主正剧烈动摇中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.44,0:16:41.19,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,在平定这两国的同时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.36,0:16:43.24,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,向联合王国的伊斯梅亚进军
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.07,0:16:45.65,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,抵达之后召回军队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.90,0:16:49.28,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,希望各位能直接前往哈鲁西亚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.45,0:16:52.24,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,拉席克大人和提欧大人一同前往弗维斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.70,0:16:55.04,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,大部队则朝克劳维斯进军
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.16,0:16:56.21,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.79,0:17:00.71,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,用战争与宣称留在同盟的君生分出胜负
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.25,0:17:03.59,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,有意加入联盟的君生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.67,0:17:05.22,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,就请他们加入大部队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.84,0:17:10.76,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉会变成一支庞大的部队啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.31,0:17:13.31,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,就把弗维斯和克劳维斯两国
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.02,0:17:16.02,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,当作君主会议的见面礼好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.25,0:17:42.46,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我等特来加入联合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.84,0:17:45.17,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,弗维斯王杰里科・奈特梅亚大人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.84,0:17:48.18,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎决心留在同盟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.51,0:17:50.05,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,真是伟大的觉悟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.26,0:17:52.18,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,其余的君主们的动向呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.47,0:17:56.48,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,东北方有归属弗维斯王的君主布拉尼斯男爵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.23,0:17:59.52,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,固守在坚固的城池中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.19,0:18:01.36,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,布拉尼斯啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.81,0:18:05.19,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,貌似人们都传那人是弗维斯的毒蛇啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.94,0:18:11.49,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,独立君主拉德班男爵决心站在弗维斯的一边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.66,0:18:13.91,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,拉席克大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.20,0:18:14.99,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.87,0:18:17.54,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,进攻拉德班男爵一事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.70,0:18:19.92,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,能否交给提欧大人来办呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.50,0:18:21.21,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.63,0:18:28.38,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就去把那弗维斯的毒蛇啥的人的城抢过来好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.67,0:18:30.80,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,既然如此需要借你兵吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.26,0:18:33.60,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我一个人就够了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.02,0:18:44.57,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,把圣印交给我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.57,0:18:46.57,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,速速离开领地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.90,0:18:48.86,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,财产能带多少带多少便是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.61,0:18:54.95,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不过撤退的期限是三天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.33,0:18:57.16,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,三天之后若还留在领内
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.45,0:18:59.00,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我无法保证各位的性命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.25,0:19:00.41,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,真是目中无人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.46,0:19:02.54,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,真性急啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.62,0:19:05.38,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不如聊些有建设性的话题吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.00,0:19:09.13,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,让我一边设宴款待联合使者一边聊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.17,0:19:11.97,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我的女儿们也会好生招待您的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.76,0:19:15.14,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,达尔塔尼亚并没归属联合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.51,0:19:16.68,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,还望回复
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.06,0:19:20.06,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,的确既然连谈判的意思都没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.23,0:19:22.69,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那么聊下去也是浪费时间啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.61,0:19:26.94,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么意思呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.23,0:19:28.23,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,明知故问
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.28,0:19:32.20,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,杀了你收下你的圣印啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.61,0:19:33.74,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,布拉尼斯阁下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.99,0:19:35.78,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,用此等方式对待使者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.91,0:19:38.08,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,岂不是违反了君主道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.70,0:19:40.91,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你名叫什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.71,0:19:43.08,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我名叫尼古拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.67,0:19:45.08,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那么名叫尼古拉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.54,0:19:48.50,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你好好看着接下来发生的事便是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.96,0:19:52.13,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不会发生啥大事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.26,0:19:56.09,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,无非是一名愚蠢的君主丧命罢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.98,0:20:03.52,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,怎…怎么可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.48,0:20:09.23,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,等…等下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.57,0:20:21.12,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,想杀死毒蛇 只需刺穿准备咬过来的大口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.95,0:20:23.83,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,一…一起上…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.27,0:20:51.61,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,以一敌众的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.23,0:20:54.82,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,被包围起来更方便动手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.57,0:20:58.95,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟周围都是敌人嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.41,0:21:02.16,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,好…好强
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.56,0:21:31.82,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,看清楚了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.27,0:21:33.69,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,是…是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.07,0:21:37.28,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,塞维斯的军队终将前来接管这座城
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.36,0:21:40.62,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你向他们报告原委便是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.83,0:21:45.16,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,谨遵嘱咐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.67,0:21:54.76,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,好了我可是单枪匹马攻陷了一座城
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.05,0:21:58.72,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你会怎么办呢
